title: Pravasi_Express
exrest: Pravasi Express is a bilingual newspaper publishing from Singapore. Formed in 2012, the newspaper presents news from various categories like Singapore news, Kerala news, world news, entertainment, lifestyle, arts and culture, technology, sports and movies.
